      <title>特朗普的“美国制造”比特币是一个不可能实现的承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/trump-s-made-in-usa-bitcoin-is-a-promise-impossible-to-keep</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当唐纳德·特朗普准备兑现一长串的竞选承诺时，这位当选总统承诺确保所有剩余的比特币都是“美国制造”，这可能被证明是最难兑现的承诺之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/trump-s-made-in-usa-bitcoin-is-a-promise-impossible-to-keep</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着需求减弱、购买方式转变，美国对华石油出口减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/us-oil-exports-to-china-dwindle-as-demand-wanes-buying-shifts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国经济的变化对需求造成影响，且中国从俄罗斯和伊朗等其他国家购买了更多原油，今年美国对中国的原油出口下降了近一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/us-oil-exports-to-china-dwindle-as-demand-wanes-buying-shifts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
